{
  "stem": "25381.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they were killed, but the two sons and a daughter with the children, and their uncle, the father, their [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So he says, I'm with Yehuda-- [NON-ENGLISH] was his name, Yehuda [NON-ENGLISH] was-- I'm staying with them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So I was so shocked.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I say, he's my relative.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So he went over there underground, and he told them that he met relatives of mine.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So this man, his son, he thought this is my sister because before the war, he wanted to marry my sister.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And so he thought that she survived.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So when he came-- so I said, no, that's me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "My sister got killed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And his wife got killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he had a child nine months old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So he says, you know what?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Maybe God-- OK, you're a lot younger than him, 17 years.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So he said, you know what?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He wants to take me out from the-- from the house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So they say the Polish people-- the Polish people, they say, the owner, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "She's not anymore a Jewish girl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "That means that she's not anymore a Jewish girl.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "She is Polish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we marry her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "She's going to marry a Polish fellow, and she's going to become from ours.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They were Catholic.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And they kicked him out from the house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They didn't let him to take me to stay with them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "They kicked him out from the house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I couldn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I ran outside, and he said-- we were talking-- and he said, on the second day, he came over, and that night, while they were asleep, I opened the window, and I ran away from the house through the window, and I went with them to their forest, and I slept already with them.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then it became misery already.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
